            <abstract>
                <p>General record for the Miracles of <persName ref="PRS6418Mabaas">the saint Mabāʾa Ṣǝyon</persName>.</p>
              <p>The Miracles are listed following <bibl>
                <ptr target="bm:Budge1898MabaaSeyon"/>
              </bibl> and Mss <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML3420"/>, <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML4817"/>,
                <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML1779"/>,
                and <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmy024"/>.
                The text as currently shown follows the edition <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Budge1898MabaaSeyon"/>
                </bibl> and Mss <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML3420"/> and <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmy024"/>.</p>
            </abstract>
